9-1-1 service? 

Mr. MARTIN. Well, we have issued an order that requires satellite 
phone  providers  to  provide  a  9-1-1  service.  They  do  it  in  a  slightly 
different  way,  trying  to  recognize  they  have  a  different  technology 
and  different  technical  benefits  and  limitations,  but  yes  we  have. 
Senator  SUNUNU.  Why  not  issue  an  order  similarly  recognizing 

